Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning in Ponyville shimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.64,0:00:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning in Ponyville shines{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I know\NFor absolute certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.36,0:00:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That everything\NIs certainly fine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's the mayor en route\NTo her office{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's the sofa clerk\NSelling some quills{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.46,0:00:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.50,0:00:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My Ponyville\NIs so gentle and still{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.84,0:00:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Can things ever go wrong?\NI don't think that they will{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.93,0:00:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning in Ponyville shimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.28,0:00:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Morning in Ponyville shines{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.71,0:00:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I know\NFor absolute certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.14,0:00:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That everything is certainly...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.96,0:00:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash! That's not funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.41,0:00:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Terribly sorry, darling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I'm not good\Nwith the thundery ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Something tells me\Neverything is not going to be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Season 3 | Episode 13\NMagical Mystery Cure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.58,0:01:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Subbed by GrayJeager\NFr.Jeager@gmail.com
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,http://www.youtube.com/user/GrayJeager3\Nhttp://www.youtube.com/user/GhxBronie\Nhttp://grayjeager.blogspot.fr (french)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NWhat happened to your cutie mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever do you mean, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.27,0:01:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm simply doing what I've done\Nsince the day it first appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Does my sky look fabulous\Nor what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.98,0:02:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Too last season?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.73,0:02:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Rainbow Dash?\NWhy isn't she handling this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't know\Nwhat you had to wake me up for.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I love sleeping in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about the weather, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.20,0:02:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity had Rainbow Dash's cutie mark\Nand said this was Rainbow Dash's cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Something strange is going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.96,0:02:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!\NWhy is Rarity doing your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.37,0:02:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And what in Equestria is going on in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.26,0:02:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.05,0:02:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These animals don't listen\NNo, not one little bit{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They run around out of control\NAnd throw their hissy fits{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's up to me to stop them\N'Cause plainly you can see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got to be my destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's what\NMy cutie mark is telling me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I try to keep them laughing\NPut a smile upon their face{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But no matter what I try\NIt seems a bit of a disgrace{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to entertain them\NIt's there for all to see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got to be my destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.10,0:03:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's what\NMy cutie mark is telling me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't care much for pickin' fruit\NAnd plowin' fields ain't such a hoot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No matter what I try\NI cannot fix this busted water chute!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've got so many chores to do\NIt's no fun being me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it has to be my destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}'Cause it's what\NMy cutie mark is telling me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Lookie here at what I made\NI think that it's a dress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.25,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it doesn't look like much\NI'm under some distress{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could y'all give me a hand here\NAnd help me fix this mess?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My destiny is not pretty{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it's what\NMy cutie mark is tellin' me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.30,0:04:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in love with weather patterns\NBut the others have concerns{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For I just gave them frostbite\NOver-top of their sunburns{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.87,0:04:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to keep on trying\NFor everyone can see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's got to be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.95,0:04:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And it's what my cutie mark{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.30,0:04:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's what my cutie mark{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, it's what\NMy cutie mark is telling me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.\NThis is very, very bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?\NWhy is this happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Last night when you were taking\None of your seven-hour bubble baths,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I got a special delivery\Nfrom the princess.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Twilight Sparkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell contained\Non the last page of this book
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is Star Swirl the Bearded's\Nsecret unfinished masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,He was never able to get it right,\Nand thus abandoned it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you are the only pony\Nwho can understand and rewrite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.54,0:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Celestia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.77,0:05:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,From one to another,\Nanother to one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A mark of one's destiny\Nsingled out alone, fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.50,0:05:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't make any sense.\NIt doesn't even rhyme!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.68,0:05:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I cast the spell\Nso I could find out what it was.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But nothing seemed to happen.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.28,0:05:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I know something did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The spell has changed\Nthe Elements of Harmony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.14,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That must be why\Ntheir cutie marks are all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So just cast a counter-spell\Nto switch them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.98,0:05:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no counter-spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.23,0:05:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What about that memory spell you used\Nto fix everypony when Discord was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not their memories, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's their true selves\Nthat have been altered!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.59,0:05:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,- Zecora's cure for the Cutie Pox?\N- That won't work either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.26,0:05:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it won't be so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.77,0:05:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe our friends will grow\Nto like their new lives?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.13,0:05:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No Spike. They're not\Nwho they are meant to be anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Their destinies are now changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's all my fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to find a way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To make this all okay{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.12,0:06:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't believe this small mistake{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.32,0:06:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Could've caused so much heartache{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.65,0:06:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.66,0:06:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Losing promise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.99,0:06:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know what to do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Seeking answers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I fear I won't get through to you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh why{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Spike, what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.42,0:07:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on, Twilight,\Nyou'll figure out a way to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.44,0:07:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,These are your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.31,0:07:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.05,0:07:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And they mean more to me\Nthan anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.43,0:07:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.98,0:07:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight?\NAre you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.28,0:07:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it! I know what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.53,0:07:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I may not be able\Nto remind them of who they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can show them\Nwhat they mean to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.87,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find the part of themselves\Nthat's been lost so they can
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.28,0:07:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,help the friend\Nthey care about so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.87,0:07:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.93,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.36,0:08:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Oh... Hey, Twilight...\N- Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.86,0:08:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moving back to Cloudsdale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's wrong,\Nbut I can't seem to make anypony laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you go,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you might\Nbe willing to help Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really struggling\Nwith her animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.79,0:08:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't really know\Nanything about animals...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.25,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But you do know something\Nabout Rainbow Dash.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.94,0:08:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I know\Nthat she's a true friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.35,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll do\Nanything I can to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.73,0:08:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.11,0:08:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in here! Help!\NI'm trapped!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, Twilight! Can't you do\Nsome sort of spell to get her out?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.35,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy,\Nyou're the only one who can help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Rainbow Dash needs you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:09:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Little... woodland creatures?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that\Nyou're all very upset,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.75,0:09:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel like giving\NRainbow Dash a hard time,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but we'd all really appreciate it\Nif you'd calm down and, um,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe rest for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.88,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Uh... look!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's some nice, juicy leaves\Nfor you to munch on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.36,0:09:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And some crunchy,\Nmunchy acorns too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.80,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wouldn't you like to take a break\Nand have a little snack?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, look at that. I guess you were\Nall just cranky because you were hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.57,0:09:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you are very welcome,\Nlittle friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.23,0:09:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodness, it's like\NI can understand them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I feel strange, like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.93,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,like this is what I'm meant to do,\Nlike this is who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.95,0:09:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,My destiny!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.10,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, look!\NYour cutie mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.16,0:10:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!\NIt worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm so happy\Nyou're back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we need your help!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.18,0:10:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.54,0:10:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend will be there\NTo help them see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.57,0:10:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.03,0:10:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see the light that shines\NFrom a true, true friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.53,0:10:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, hello! Friend trapped inside,\Nremember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.37,0:10:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Rarity needs your help{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's trying hard doing\NWhat she can{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would you try\NJust give it a chance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You might find that\NYou'll start to understand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.17,0:10:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend will be there\NTo help you see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.32,0:11:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see the light that shines\NFrom a true, true friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.03,0:11:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time to explain,\Nbut we need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Applejack's trying to make dresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.50,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Say no more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.83,0:11:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Applejack needs your help{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.81,0:11:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}She's trying hard doing\NWhat she can{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.27,0:11:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Would you try\NJust give it a chance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.07,0:11:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You might find that\NYou'll start to understand{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend will be there\NTo help them see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.92,0:11:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see the light that shines\NFrom a true, true friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, what a terrible dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Or, maybe I'm still having it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Rarity, Pinkie Pie is about\Nto lose the apple farm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.70,0:12:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We need Applejack's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Lose the apple farm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well we can't let that happen,\Nnow can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.42,0:12:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Pinkie Pie is in trouble{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We need to get there\NBy her side{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.94,0:12:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can try to do\NWhat we can now{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For together we can be\NHer guide!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.35,0:12:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend will be there\NTo help them see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see the light that shines\NFrom a true, true friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's more like it,\Nwhat's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The townspeople are furious,\Nwe need the old Pinkie Pie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on it, I know just the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.54,0:12:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The townspeople need you\NThey've been sad for a while{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They march around, faces frown\NAnd never seem to smile{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:13:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And if you feel like helping\NWe'd appreciate a lot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you get up there and spread\NSome cheer from here to Canterlot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on ponies,\NI wanna see you smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A friend will be there\NTo help them see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.26,0:13:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true, true friend\NHelps a friend in need{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see the light\N(to see the light){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That shines\N(that shines){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}From a true, true friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mark of one's destiny,\Nsingled out alone, fulfilled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.44,0:13:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand now,\NI know how to fix the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,From all of us together,\Ntogether we are friends,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.55,0:13:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,with the marks of our destinies made one,\Nthere is magic without end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Where am I?\NWhat is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Twilight.\NI knew you could do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.98,0:14:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! I don't understand.\NWhat did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.01,0:14:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You did something today\Nthat's never been done before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:15:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Something even a great unicorn like\NStar Swirl the Bearded was not able to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.69,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he did not understand\Nfriendship like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.58,0:15:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The lessons you've learned here in Ponyville\Nhave taught you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.86,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You have proven that you're ready,\NTwilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.94,0:15:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ready? Ready for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.60,0:15:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've come such a long, long way{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.57,0:15:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I've watched you\NFrom that very first day{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see how you might grow{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.40,0:15:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see what you might do{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see what you've been through{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And all the ways\NYou've made me proud of you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.42,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's time now\NFor a new change to come{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.09,0:16:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've grown up\NAnd your new life has begun{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To go where you will go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To see what you will see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To find what you will be{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For it's time for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To fulfill your destiny{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.55,0:16:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight...? Is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.71,0:17:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I've never seen\Nanything like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight's got wings! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A new flying buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you've become an alicorn.\NI didn't even know that was possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.36,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Alicorn party!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.67,0:17:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... you look just like a princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.41,0:17:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because she is a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.49,0:17:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,A princess?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you've come to Ponyville,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.37,0:17:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,you've displayed the charity, compassion,\Ndevotion, integrity, optimism,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and of course,\Nthe leadership of a true princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.41,0:17:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But... does this mean\NI won't be your student anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.49,0:17:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the same way as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.67,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll still be here to help and guide you,\Nbut we're all your students now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.35,0:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You are an inspiration to us all,\NTwilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But... what do I do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a book about\Nbeing a princess I should read?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.42,0:18:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be time\Nfor all of that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.84,0:18:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We are gathered here today\Nin celebration of a momentous occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.19,0:18:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,My most faithful student,\NTwilight Sparkle,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,has done many extraordinary things\Nsince she's lived in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.59,0:18:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She even helped reunite me\Nwith my sister, Princess Luna.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, Twilight Sparkle\Ndid something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.82,0:18:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She created new magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.62,0:18:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,proving without a doubt\Nthat she is ready
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.06,0:18:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,to be crowned\NEquestria's newest princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Fillies and gentlecolts,\Nmay I present for the very first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.91,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight Sparkle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thou Princess Twilight cometh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.06,0:19:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Behold, behold{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A Princess here before us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Behold, behold, behold{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.46,0:19:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Behold, behold\N(behold, behold){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Princess Twilight cometh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.09,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Behold, behold\N(behold, behold){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.42,0:19:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Princess is\N(the Princess is){\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.21,0:19:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A little while ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.01,0:19:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,my teacher and mentor Princess Celestia\Nsent me to live in Ponyville.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.42,0:19:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She sent me to study friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.88,0:19:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,which is something\NI didn't really care much about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.34,0:20:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, on a day like today,\NI can honestly say
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be standing here\Nif it weren't for the friendships
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.21,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made with all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Each one of you taught me something\Nabout friendship, and for that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.31,0:20:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I will always be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I consider myself\Nthe luckiest pony in Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, friends.\NThank you, everypony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.25,0:20:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight! I'm so proud of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.36,0:20:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.71,0:20:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not,\Nit's... it's liquid pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Totally different thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Best coronation day ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.47,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,- We love you, Twilight.\N- I love you too, girls!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The light in Equestria shimmers{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.37,0:21:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Life in Equestria shines{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I know for absolute certain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.37,0:21:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, everything is going to{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be fine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.24,0:21:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, fine{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!\NEverything's gonna be just fine!
